      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening model with yield stress 880 MPa and tangent modulus 1.1 GPa captures the load-displacement response through yield. Sensitivity analysis showed frictionless versus frictional contact (mu=0.2) changed construct stiffness by <0.4%, supporting the simplified contact assumption."
