      "rationale": "All testing performed at a single crosshead displacement rate of 5 mm/min per ASTM F1717 standard. A second loading rate was not evaluated. This single-condition limitation reduces the achieved level to 2, below the required level of 3. The gap is acknowledged and accepted given the quasi-static nature of the clinical loading scenario, but represents a documented shortfall in the credibility evidence."
